cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.CR 

This paper deals with natural language processing techniques to extract locations from microblogs during emergencies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and cybernetics (cs.CY) as it deals with monitoring and analyzing emergency situations. Additionally, the paper involves security and privacy (cs.CR) as it deals with sensitive information during emergencies.
